            "color_icon": "rgba(0,0,0,0)",
            "svg-code": "",
            "text": "<p>At Fenceworks, we do things a little differently — no surprise boxes dumped on your driveway. We offer white-glove installation to ensure your playset is expertly assembled and ready for play.</p><ul><li><strong>White-Glove Installation:</strong> If you’re within 60 miles of our Northbrook office, our team will handle delivery and installation with care. With 58+ years of experience and in-depth knowledge of city codes, we make sure everything is set up safely and correctly.</li><li><strong>Outside Our Service Area?</strong> If you’re beyond 60 miles, additional fees may apply. Please call us at <a href=\"tel:847-432-0900\" title=\"tel:847-432-0900\">847-432-0900</a> or email <a href=\"mailto:contact@theguyon41.com\" title=\"mailto:contact@theguyon41.com\">contact@theguyon41.com</a> to get a custom installation quote.<br/><br/></li></ul><p><strong>Questions?</strong> Reach out anytime. We’re here to help every step of the way.</p>",
